{"title":"长津会亲人","authors":["张致祥"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长津会亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张致祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长津湖水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁量过有多深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面蕴蓄着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生死与共的战友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过黄草岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长津会亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下碣隅里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人列队相迎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语和鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香甜醉人心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人为指点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼敌扬威名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对面飞鹤高地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨根思献出青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左边土丘上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建有烈士陵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏长青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难喻我们的友情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黛莱红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比不上我们火热的心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“泗水里”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改名“解放区”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“柳漂里”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在叫“中华里”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了纪念伟大的友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人民永远想念中国兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民也永远想念朝鲜兄弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜先驱者们的鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洒在中国的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们用生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援了中国的解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里的松林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远飘着清香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对共同敌人的标语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨迹还留在树干上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一堆堆篝火的灰烬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是革命圣火的遗迹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在熊熊的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经撕破夜空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把东方照亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜血是宝贵的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命是宝贵的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命大业和革命友情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是更宝贵的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以洒尽热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献出生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"市侩们和那些庸庸碌碌的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不能懂得无产阶级战友之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样的交情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说不完的往事啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件件、一桩桩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像久别的旧友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉不尽的衷肠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了亲人会见干杯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒浇在心头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红到脸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红到眼上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情梗塞住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了嘴边的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它化成热泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点滴滴流下来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚才还是相见的欢欣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了别意离情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲人送别我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指着黄草岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迸出一句话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫叶红时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄草岭最美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枫叶红时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望你们再来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们驰车在黄草岭的高原上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原是那样粗犷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们是那样热情、豪放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夕阳下山头白雪在闪闪发光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想立即变成一个巨人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用粗壮的臂膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这里的一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱在我的怀里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧贴在我的心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1962年6月25日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}